FBIS4-7326 "dreas083_g_94004" FBIS-EAS-94-083 Daily Report 27 Apr 1994 SOUTHEAST ASIA Burma Education Minister Joins Prime Minister's Office Education Minister Joins Prime Minister's Office BK2704153094 Rangoon Radio Burma in Burmese 1330 GMT 27 Apr 94 BK2704153094 Rangoon Radio Burma Burmese BFN [Declaration No. 3/94 of the State Law and Order Restoration Council; issued 27 April] [Text] Change of portfolio of cabinet minister. The State Law and Order Restoration Council [SLORC] has transferred Education Minister Colonel Pe Thein to the portfolio of minister of prime minister's office. By the authority vested in me, Signed; Khin Nyunt, lieutenant general, secretary-1 of the SLORC.
